## Summary
This documentation describes the Apxor destination integration with Amplitude, which allows syncing user cohorts from Amplitude to Apxor for creating personalized in-app nudges and messages based on user behavior data, with step-by-step setup instructions for both platforms and specific use cases for onboarding, feature adoption, and user activation.

